  "id": "api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe",
  "title": "DeprecatedCurrencyPipe",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L124-L160\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts#L124-L160\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe\", \"name\": \"DeprecatedCurrencyPipe\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"deprecatedcurrencypipe\">DeprecatedCurrencyPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#deprecatedcurrencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Formats a number as currency using locale rules.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"pipe-overview\">\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">{{ value_expression | <span class=\"kwd nocode\">currency</span> [ : currencyCode [ : symbolDisplay [ : digits ] ] ] }}</code-example>\n\n  \n  <h2 id=\"input-value\">输入值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#input-value\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>value</td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>any</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  \n  \n  <h2 id=\"parameters\">参数<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#parameters\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>currencyCode</td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-result=\"\">可选. 默认值是 <code>'USD'</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>symbolDisplay</td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>boolean</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-result=\"\">可选. 默认值是 <code>false</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>digits</td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-result=\"\">可选. 默认值是 <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">Use <code>currency</code> to format a number as currency.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>currencyCode</code> is the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a> currency code, such\nas <code>USD</code> for the US dollar and <code>EUR</code> for the euro.</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>symbolDisplay</code> is a boolean indicating whether to use the currency symbol or code.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>true</code>: use symbol (e.g. <code>$</code>).</li>\n<li><code>false</code>(default): use code (e.g. <code>USD</code>).</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>digitInfo</code> See <a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a> for detailed description.</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">WARNING: this pipe uses the Internationalization API which is not yet available in all browsers\nand may require a polyfill. See <a href=\"guide/browser-support\">Browser Support</a> for details.</p>\n<h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'deprecated-currency-pipe',\n  <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `&#x3C;div>\n    &#x3C;!--output 'CAD0.26'-->\n    &#x3C;p>A: {{<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> | currency:'CAD'}}&#x3C;/p>\n\n    &#x3C;!--output '$0,001.35'-->\n    &#x3C;p>B: {{b | currency:'CAD':true:'4.2-2'}}&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;/div>`\n})\nexport class DeprecatedCurrencyPipeComponent {\n  <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a>: number = 0.259;\n  b: number = 1.3495;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/browser-support\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#deprecatedcurrencypipe\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#description\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#example\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#input-value\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#parameters\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#template\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - guide/browser-support\n - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L124-L160\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts#L124-L160\n-->"
